reviewText: If you are interested in Swedish culture this film is for you.  A bit obscure and I admit it took me two viewings topick up on what was going on.  Alex Skarsgard fans (me) love it

If you are a true Alexander Skarsgard fan, and have purchased a region 2 DVD player, as I have, you will enjoy this video immensely. It shows a younger Alex in a role much different from his more serious endeavors that have been released in the U.S. It is very entertaining and once again showcases the talent of this versatile actor. I laughed my ass off at certain scenes.
